on and telephone number is listed in the State Government section of your telephone directory Effective July 1 2004 the Department of Developmental Services DDS will be responsible for administration of the Habilitation Services Program currently administered by the DOR This transfer of responsibility was required by the Fiscal Year 2003 04 Budget Bill Information regarding the status of the transfer is available at the following links VocationalSvcs DDS DOR Comparison cfm Comparison of Program Elements between DOR Work Programs and DDS Day Programs Habilitation Services Program Transfer Progress Report The Habilitation Services Program Transfer Progress Report gives a monthly update on the status of the Habilitation Transfer from DOR to DDS VocationalSvcs PDF Hab Transfer Report 6 12 03 pdf Habilitation Transfer Update June 12 2003 pdf PDF VocationalSvcs PDF Hab Progress Report 7 8 03 pdf Habilitation Transfer Update July 8 2003 pdf PDF VocationalSvcs PDF Hab Progress Report 8 22 03 pdf Habilitation Transfer Update August 22 2003 pdf PDF VocationalSvcs PDF Hab Progress Report 9 16 03 pdf Habilitation Transfer Update September 16 2003 pdf PDF VocationalSvcs PDF Hab Progress Report 10 10 03 pdf Habilitation Transfer Update October 10 2003 pdf PDF VocationalSvcs PDF Hab Map pdf Habilitation Provider Distribution Map pdf PDF The Habilitation Provider Distribution Map shows the number of Habilitation Providers per county My CA Related Links DayProgram day main cfm Day Program Services DayProgram day edsvs cfm Educational Services VocationalSvcs voc habsvs cfm Habilitation Services VocationalSvcs voc SupEmp cfm Supported Employment Services VocationalSvcs voc WkAct cfm Work Activity Programs Services Featured Links autism autism main cfm Autism factsstats factbook cfm DDS Fact Books publications reports publications cfm Publications and Other Resources calendar calendar main cfm Community Training Event Calendar publications lantermanactguide cfm Consumer s Guide to the 